quiz.question:
以下 SQL 在默认配置下（innodb_ft_min_token_size=3，未使用 ngram 解析器）执行后，最可能的结果是什么？

```sql
CREATE TABLE docs (id INT PRIMARY KEY, body TEXT, FULLTEXT(body)) ENGINE=InnoDB;
INSERT INTO docs VALUES (1, 'Go is a fast language'), (2, 'Java is popular');
SELECT * FROM docs WHERE MATCH(body) AGAINST('Go' IN NATURAL LANGUAGE MODE);
```
